<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>At the moment the client hides SoapClient's SOAP header functions/calls, which are needed in a lot of SOAP applications.</p>

<p>Could these be added in some form?</p>

<p>SoapClient accepts SOAP request headers in its SoapClient-&gt;__setSoapHeaders() function, and both request and response ones in its more advanced SOAP calls SoapClient-&gt;__soapCall()</p>

